1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="16"><font color="#8b7d91">Dorm 1\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hDorm 2\h\h\h\h\h\h\hDorm 3</font></font></font></font>

2
00:00:00,970 --> 00:00:03,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Listen up, punks.</font>

3
00:00:03,590 --> 00:00:06,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The chicken fight coming up
 is the last event of the day.</font>

4
00:00:06,960 --> 00:00:09,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We are seven points away from the lead.</font>

5
00:00:09,700 --> 00:00:11,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We still have a chance.</font>

6
00:00:11,360 --> 00:00:12,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's do this!</font>

7
00:00:12,610 --> 00:00:15,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right!</font>

8
00:01:46,640 --> 00:01:49,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ladies and gentlemen, the event
we've all been waiting for!</font>

9
00:01:49,290 --> 00:01:52,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Today's highlight: the chicken fight!</i></font>

10
00:01:53,310 --> 00:01:57,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I didn't know this wasn't just a race!</i></font>

11
00:01:57,640 --> 00:02:01,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dorm 1 is in blue bandannas, 
Dorm 2 in white, and Dorm 3 in red.</font>

12
00:02:02,150 --> 00:02:05,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Anyone who gets theirs taken
is out of the game.</i></font>

13
00:02:05,690 --> 00:02:07,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Tennoji!</i></font>

14
00:02:07,200 --> 00:02:08,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We won't let you win!</i></font>

15
00:02:09,480 --> 00:02:10,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Begin!</font>

16
00:02:11,850 --> 00:02:14,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Fierce skirmishes are 
breaking out everywhere!</i></font>

17
00:02:14,450 --> 00:02:16,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nakatsu, to the right!</font>

18
00:02:16,060 --> 00:02:16,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Got it!</font>

19
00:02:19,740 --> 00:02:21,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">First one!</font>

20
00:02:25,420 --> 00:02:27,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's eat or be eaten!</i></font>

21
00:02:27,220 --> 00:02:30,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is a truly fierce, manly showdown!</i></font>

22
00:02:30,510 --> 00:02:31,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where's Tennoji?</font>

23
00:02:43,680 --> 00:02:44,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What's this?!</i></font>

24
00:02:44,500 --> 00:02:46,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Dorm 2's attacker has 
fallen from his horse!</i></font>

25
00:02:48,360 --> 00:02:54,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Arial"><b><font color="#898091">Medical Tent</font></b></font></font>

26
00:02:48,700 --> 00:02:51,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You got away with some 
minor scrapes and bruises.</font>

27
00:02:51,640 --> 00:02:54,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know you were only
 trying to help a friend,</font>

28
00:02:55,120 --> 00:02:58,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I can't believe two grown 
boys got crushed like that.</font>

29
00:02:59,100 --> 00:03:00,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Put a sock in it.</font>

30
00:03:01,180 --> 00:03:03,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-Thanks.</font>

31
00:03:03,240 --> 00:03:04,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And sorry.</font>

32
00:03:04,270 --> 00:03:05,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine, it's fine.</font>

33
00:03:05,260 --> 00:03:06,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't sweat it.</font>

34
00:03:06,120 --> 00:03:07,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right, Izumi?</font>

35
00:03:07,440 --> 00:03:08,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure.</font>

36
00:03:08,720 --> 00:03:11,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">More importantly, are you all right?</font>

37
00:03:11,640 --> 00:03:13,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, I'm fine. Totally fine.</font>

38
00:03:13,440 --> 00:03:14,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just a scratch.</font>

39
00:03:15,280 --> 00:03:17,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But that guy from Dorm 1...</i></font>

40
00:03:17,600 --> 00:03:19,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That was definitely on purpose.</i></font>

41
00:03:20,360 --> 00:03:23,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If Sano and Nakatsu hadn't protected me...</i></font>

42
00:03:27,760 --> 00:03:32,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, well, Dorm 1 beat the 
pants off of Dorm 2 today.</font>

43
00:03:28,930 --> 00:03:32,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Impact">{\an8}<font color="#ce526a">Nanba-senpai?</font></font></font>

44
00:03:28,930 --> 00:03:32,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><b><font size="18">{\an8}<font color="#958f8c">Conference Room</font></font></b></font></font>

45
00:03:32,310 --> 00:03:38,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="16"><font color="#878685"><b>Dorm 1</b></font></font></font></font>

46
00:03:32,310 --> 00:03:38,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="16"><font color="#878685"><b>Dorm 2</b></font></font></font></font>

47
00:03:32,310 --> 00:03:38,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="16"><font color="#878685"><b>Dorm 3</b></font></font></font></font>

48
00:03:32,700 --> 00:03:34,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've got two days left.</font>

49
00:03:34,620 --> 00:03:38,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course, the arts-focused Dorm 3
 is planning a comeback of their own.</font>

50
00:03:38,570 --> 00:03:41,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can only compete with good ideas!</font>

51
00:03:41,460 --> 00:03:42,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our first-years have an arcade.</font>

52
00:03:42,830 --> 00:03:44,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our second-years, a themed café.</font>

53
00:03:44,440 --> 00:03:47,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And us third-years, a mystery show.</font>

54
00:03:48,140 --> 00:03:49,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No holding back.</font>

55
00:03:49,880 --> 00:03:51,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go all out.</font>

56
00:03:53,090 --> 00:03:54,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I felt it...</font>

57
00:03:54,770 --> 00:03:56,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, he's ready to kill.</font>

58
00:03:58,410 --> 00:04:00,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry!</font>

59
00:04:00,130 --> 00:04:01,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You all came up with good ideas,</font>

60
00:04:01,960 --> 00:04:05,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so just keep up the good work 
and rake in the student and public votes!</font>

61
00:04:06,150 --> 00:04:08,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn that Nanba.</font>

62
00:04:09,520 --> 00:04:11,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How about sparing a single thought for us?</font>

63
00:04:13,360 --> 00:04:14,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ow!</font>

64
00:04:14,490 --> 00:04:15,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you okay?</font>

65
00:04:15,700 --> 00:04:16,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me see it.</font>

66
00:04:18,920 --> 00:04:20,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, good.</font>

67
00:04:20,210 --> 00:04:21,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not swollen.</font>

68
00:04:22,710 --> 00:04:24,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Does it still hurt?</font>

69
00:04:27,920 --> 00:04:29,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry.</font>

70
00:04:29,270 --> 00:04:31,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was my fault.</font>

71
00:04:32,970 --> 00:04:35,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's nothing serious.</font>

72
00:04:35,560 --> 00:04:39,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-Anyway, during the chicken fight,</font>

73
00:04:39,210 --> 00:04:40,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that guy did that on purpose, right?</font>

74
00:04:40,940 --> 00:04:42,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You think they have it out for you?</font>

75
00:04:42,980 --> 00:04:44,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why me, though?</font>

76
00:04:44,950 --> 00:04:46,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing comes to mind?</font>

77
00:04:52,130 --> 00:04:53,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

78
00:04:53,570 --> 00:04:55,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right.</font>

79
00:04:55,240 --> 00:04:59,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, can't hurt to be cautious, 
so keep an eye out.</font>

80
00:04:59,730 --> 00:05:00,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

81
00:05:00,990 --> 00:05:04,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I mean, it's not even like 
he really did anything to me.</i></font>

82
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:05,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't just assume he's behind it.</i></font>

83
00:05:06,340 --> 00:05:08,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, I'm gonna go shower.</font>

84
00:05:12,340 --> 00:05:15,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's hiding something from me again.</i></font>

85
00:05:15,840 --> 00:05:17,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Since it's some fool from Dorm 1,</i></font>

86
00:05:17,350 --> 00:05:19,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>it's either that moron Tennoji
 or one of his goons.</i></font>

87
00:05:20,690 --> 00:05:24,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This leaves me no choice 
but to be on the lookout.</i></font>

88
00:05:26,940 --> 00:05:28,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wait, why do I have to do that?</i></font>

89
00:05:30,090 --> 00:05:32,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Guess that's just how it goes.</i></font>

90
00:05:32,060 --> 00:05:33,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Got it. Got it.</i></font>

91
00:05:36,610 --> 00:05:39,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial Black"><font color="#efff9f">MärChange</font></font></font>

92
00:05:37,110 --> 00:05:39,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ta-da!</font>

93
00:05:39,980 --> 00:05:41,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you think?</font>

94
00:05:41,020 --> 00:05:42,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't get outed!</i></font>

95
00:05:42,310 --> 00:05:43,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't get outed!</i></font>

96
00:05:47,750 --> 00:05:49,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What?</font>

97
00:05:49,180 --> 00:05:50,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it that weird?</font>

98
00:05:50,260 --> 00:05:54,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know it's too late, but it's 
really a shame about you two.</font>

99
00:05:54,260 --> 00:05:56,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't say that so genuinely.</font>

100
00:05:56,450 --> 00:05:59,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, seriously! 
Just give us a normal compliment.</font>

101
00:05:59,650 --> 00:06:02,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yo, Ashiya! Looking good!</font>

102
00:06:02,140 --> 00:06:03,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Noe? Sekime?</font>

103
00:06:03,840 --> 00:06:04,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey!</font>

104
00:06:08,600 --> 00:06:10,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Noe!</font>

105
00:06:10,010 --> 00:06:12,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This thing is hella tight!</font>

106
00:06:12,150 --> 00:06:13,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Talk about bulky!</i></font>

107
00:06:14,540 --> 00:06:16,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right, man.</font>

108
00:06:16,110 --> 00:06:18,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll let it out under the arms,
 so hold still.</font>

109
00:06:18,490 --> 00:06:22,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Noe, you're, like, scary good 
at making this stuff.</font>

110
00:06:26,010 --> 00:06:28,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>H-How cute!</i></font>

111
00:06:30,670 --> 00:06:32,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nakatsu, you dumbass!</font>

112
00:06:32,720 --> 00:06:34,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're gonna get your dress all dirty!</font>

113
00:06:36,090 --> 00:06:37,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Where's Sano?</font>

114
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:39,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's getting ready!</font>

115
00:06:44,530 --> 00:06:46,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm coming in!</font>

116
00:06:48,860 --> 00:06:50,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where's my wig?!</font>

117
00:06:52,310 --> 00:06:55,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I-I hope Sano doesn't look like that.</i></font>

118
00:06:55,860 --> 00:06:56,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't move.</font>

119
00:06:56,990 --> 00:06:58,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll screw up your eyeliner.</font>

120
00:07:00,200 --> 00:07:01,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, all done.</font>

121
00:07:01,620 --> 00:07:03,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow, Sano!</font>

122
00:07:06,830 --> 00:07:08,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right, who's up next?</font>

123
00:07:08,680 --> 00:07:09,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me!</font>

124
00:07:09,780 --> 00:07:12,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}We've got no time, so we'll 
skip right to the foundation.</font>

125
00:07:11,580 --> 00:07:15,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow, how pretty! Beautiful!</font>

126
00:07:16,060 --> 00:07:16,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yo.</font>

127
00:07:17,710 --> 00:07:19,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What costume is that?</font>

128
00:07:19,340 --> 00:07:21,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yang Guifei, apparently.</font>

129
00:07:21,680 --> 00:07:23,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you stop staring like that?</font>

130
00:07:23,440 --> 00:07:24,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aw, what's the harm?</font>

131
00:07:24,800 --> 00:07:26,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You look so good!</font>

132
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:27,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dude...</font>

133
00:07:27,550 --> 00:07:30,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Day two of the school festival 
is now officially open!</i></font>

134
00:07:33,240 --> 00:07:34,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have a blast!</font>

135
00:07:34,290 --> 00:07:35,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Buy your tickets here!</font>

136
00:07:35,730 --> 00:07:37,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="20"><font face="Arial Black"><font color="#efff9f">MärChange</font></font></font></font>

137
00:07:38,400 --> 00:07:40,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome!</font>

138
00:07:40,240 --> 00:07:42,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Party of three over here!</font>

139
00:07:43,520 --> 00:07:45,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I shall show you to your table.</font>

140
00:07:46,600 --> 00:07:49,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This <i>is</i> an all-boys school, right?</font>

141
00:07:49,870 --> 00:07:51,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Got it!</font>

142
00:07:51,070 --> 00:07:52,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Coming right up!</font>

143
00:07:51,690 --> 00:07:52,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ready to order?</font>

144
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:54,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks good, huh?</font>

145
00:07:54,630 --> 00:07:55,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks!</font>

146
00:07:56,320 --> 00:08:00,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The beauty pageant contestants have been 
posted in the lobby of the western wing.</i></font>

147
00:08:00,500 --> 00:08:05,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Tomorrow's twelve finalists 
will be determined by today's vote.</i></font>

148
00:08:04,900 --> 00:08:07,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial Black"><font color="#312f2f">23 Ashiya Mizuki</font></font></font>

149
00:08:05,420 --> 00:08:07,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Make sure to cast yours!</i></font>

150
00:08:08,270 --> 00:08:13,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know, man. I feel like this 
year's contestants are a cut above.</font>

151
00:08:13,230 --> 00:08:14,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can say that again.</font>

152
00:08:15,270 --> 00:08:18,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, they said there's a 
really cute girl in 2-C.</font>

153
00:08:18,770 --> 00:08:20,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No way! For real? We gotta go!</font>

154
00:08:20,950 --> 00:08:22,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's still a guy, dumbass.</font>

155
00:08:23,770 --> 00:08:25,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Two iced teas, please!</font>

156
00:08:25,440 --> 00:08:27,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I need a coffee.</font>

157
00:08:27,310 --> 00:08:28,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">On it!</font>

158
00:08:28,660 --> 00:08:30,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello! I'm with the executive committee.</font>

159
00:08:30,880 --> 00:08:34,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've come to do a survey of the 
beauty pageant contestants.</font>

160
00:08:36,080 --> 00:08:40,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're Ashiya-kun, contestant 23, 
and Nakao-kun, contestant 18, correct?</font>

161
00:08:40,370 --> 00:08:41,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes!</font>

162
00:08:40,370 --> 00:08:41,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Yeah...</font>

163
00:08:41,370 --> 00:08:44,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The votes for you two are coming in hot!</font>

164
00:08:44,700 --> 00:08:47,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, let's hear your measurements!</font>

165
00:08:47,340 --> 00:08:48,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

166
00:08:48,570 --> 00:08:49,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go on!</font>

167
00:08:49,560 --> 00:08:53,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, from the top, I'm 74-60-78.</font>

168
00:08:53,840 --> 00:08:56,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, but don't tell anyone!</font>

169
00:08:56,340 --> 00:08:57,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you, Ashiya-kun?</font>

170
00:08:57,760 --> 00:09:00,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Er, well... I'm, uh...</font>

171
00:09:01,040 --> 00:09:02,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See you!</font>

172
00:09:02,740 --> 00:09:04,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-That's none of your...</font>

173
00:09:04,190 --> 00:09:05,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, Ashiya-kun?</font>

174
00:09:05,450 --> 00:09:07,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...business!</font>

175
00:09:08,390 --> 00:09:10,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He sure is fast!</font>

176
00:09:10,700 --> 00:09:12,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Guess that's that.</font>

177
00:09:12,300 --> 00:09:14,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shall we move on to the next class?</font>

178
00:09:15,840 --> 00:09:18,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't he supposed to be injured?</font>

179
00:09:18,020 --> 00:09:19,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like he's in top form.</font>

180
00:09:19,760 --> 00:09:20,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Calm down.</font>

181
00:09:20,790 --> 00:09:24,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We just need to make sure he's out of
 the 2,000-meter race on the final day.</font>

182
00:09:24,830 --> 00:09:27,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, and we've got plenty
 of ways to do that.</font>

183
00:09:32,550 --> 00:09:36,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, I never should've
 entered the beauty pageant.</font>

184
00:09:36,160 --> 00:09:37,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you talking about?</font>

185
00:09:41,010 --> 00:09:43,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Crap! Those two again?</font>

186
00:09:45,010 --> 00:09:47,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm not even trying to spy on them.</i></font>

187
00:09:47,990 --> 00:09:49,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why are they always...</i></font>

188
00:09:54,240 --> 00:09:55,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">D-Doctor?</font>

189
00:09:56,780 --> 00:09:58,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello there, Ashiya.</font>

190
00:09:58,060 --> 00:10:00,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Love the outfit.</font>

191
00:10:00,410 --> 00:10:03,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing out here?</font>

192
00:10:03,170 --> 00:10:05,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was just taking a little break,</font>

193
00:10:05,630 --> 00:10:07,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but then I found myself
 rooted to the spot.</font>

194
00:10:07,950 --> 00:10:09,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"A little break"?!</font>

195
00:10:09,420 --> 00:10:12,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that what a teacher calls 
drinking on the clock?!</font>

196
00:10:12,840 --> 00:10:14,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've got nothing better to do.</font>

197
00:10:14,800 --> 00:10:17,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm just supposed to accept that?</font>

198
00:10:18,050 --> 00:10:20,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're the one who up and disappeared!</font>

199
00:10:20,840 --> 00:10:23,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And now you come back
 and hit me with <i>that</i>?</font>

200
00:10:23,690 --> 00:10:25,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cut the crap!</font>

201
00:10:25,260 --> 00:10:26,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Minami...</font>

202
00:10:28,700 --> 00:10:29,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doctor?</font>

203
00:10:37,070 --> 00:10:40,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So he's still not over it, I see.</font>

204
00:10:41,200 --> 00:10:45,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That girl was Minami's tutor in his last
year of middle school. They dated.</font>

205
00:10:45,700 --> 00:10:47,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pretty sure it wasn't until they broke up</font>

206
00:10:47,910 --> 00:10:50,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that he started acting
 like somewhat of a player.</font>

207
00:10:51,330 --> 00:10:52,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Nanba-senpai...</i></font>

208
00:10:53,210 --> 00:10:57,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you have any idea what I've 
been going through since you left?</font>

209
00:10:57,540 --> 00:10:59,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am so sorry.</font>

210
00:10:59,090 --> 00:11:02,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know there's no excuse for what I did...</font>

211
00:11:02,060 --> 00:11:04,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I really did love you.</font>

212
00:11:04,670 --> 00:11:06,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I did.</font>

213
00:11:06,060 --> 00:11:07,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please believe me.</font>

214
00:11:07,230 --> 00:11:09,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Believe you? What the hell 
am I supposed to believe?!</font>

215
00:11:10,510 --> 00:11:11,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Minami...</font>

216
00:11:11,780 --> 00:11:13,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're leaving me.</font>

217
00:11:13,530 --> 00:11:16,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You... You're abandoning me!</font>

218
00:11:16,810 --> 00:11:18,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Minami, let me go!</font>

219
00:11:32,690 --> 00:11:33,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go.</font>

220
00:11:34,780 --> 00:11:36,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go wherever it is you're going.</font>

221
00:11:38,750 --> 00:11:39,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who's there?!</font>

222
00:11:39,830 --> 00:11:41,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh no!</i></font>

223
00:11:42,220 --> 00:11:43,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The doctor's gone!</i></font>

224
00:11:44,550 --> 00:11:45,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Minami.</font>

225
00:11:46,660 --> 00:11:50,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You and I were just kids back then.</font>

226
00:11:52,780 --> 00:11:53,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Goodbye.</font>

227
00:11:59,990 --> 00:12:01,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who's there?</font>

228
00:12:05,260 --> 00:12:07,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a pathetic sight to witness.</font>

229
00:12:07,940 --> 00:12:10,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So... who was she?</font>

230
00:12:10,980 --> 00:12:14,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Someone who threw me away three years ago.</font>

231
00:12:14,050 --> 00:12:16,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The first woman I ever fell in love with.</font>

232
00:12:17,530 --> 00:12:21,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That "if we can be together, 
I don't need anything else" kind of love.</font>

233
00:12:22,200 --> 00:12:25,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But one day, she disappeared 
without a single word.</font>

234
00:12:25,520 --> 00:12:31,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought I'd forgotten her 
and everything about her.</font>

235
00:12:32,060 --> 00:12:36,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I saw her again, I was forced 
to admit that wasn't true.</font>

236
00:12:37,310 --> 00:12:39,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She told me she's getting married.</font>

237
00:12:43,870 --> 00:12:48,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The guy she's marrying
 is about twice my age.</font>

238
00:12:49,020 --> 00:12:52,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't even know what to say.</i></font>

239
00:12:53,530 --> 00:12:57,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ashiya, can I just ask you for one thing?</font>

240
00:12:57,650 --> 00:13:00,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where the hell did he go?</font>

241
00:13:04,440 --> 00:13:06,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can I have a hug?</font>

242
00:13:09,290 --> 00:13:11,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just this once.</font>

243
00:13:11,020 --> 00:13:12,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks.</font>

244
00:13:29,190 --> 00:13:30,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry.</font>

245
00:13:30,850 --> 00:13:32,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nanba-senpai...</font>

246
00:13:32,870 --> 00:13:34,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just kidding!</font>

247
00:13:34,600 --> 00:13:35,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Senpai!</font>

248
00:13:36,250 --> 00:13:39,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You just look so adorable,</font>

249
00:13:39,760 --> 00:13:45,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I figured a womanizer like myself 
couldn't let this one chance slip away!</font>

250
00:13:45,630 --> 00:13:46,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you annoyed?</font>

251
00:13:47,190 --> 00:13:48,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not at all.</font>

252
00:13:48,750 --> 00:13:51,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's so like you, I'm impressed.</font>

253
00:13:54,750 --> 00:13:58,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, Ashiya, are you in love 
with anyone right now?</font>

254
00:13:59,160 --> 00:14:01,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nice and honest.</font>

255
00:14:01,470 --> 00:14:02,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cherish it.</font>

256
00:14:03,680 --> 00:14:06,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll never be in love like this again.</font>

257
00:14:09,070 --> 00:14:10,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once this love is over,</font>

258
00:14:10,550 --> 00:14:13,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you might fall in love with someone else,</font>

259
00:14:13,040 --> 00:14:15,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but the love will never be the same.</font>

260
00:14:17,660 --> 00:14:19,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Love also matures.</font>

261
00:14:20,530 --> 00:14:23,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which is why it must be tended with care.</font>

262
00:14:23,770 --> 00:14:25,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So that your feelings may bloom.</font>

263
00:14:26,630 --> 00:14:29,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Speaking of, I really need to grow up.</font>

264
00:14:31,140 --> 00:14:34,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Hey, Ashiya Mizuki!</i></font>

265
00:14:34,180 --> 00:14:36,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}How long are you going to play hooky?!</i></font>

266
00:14:35,500 --> 00:14:36,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nakao-kun?!</font>

267
00:14:37,410 --> 00:14:39,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I've got to get back.</font>

268
00:14:37,410 --> 00:14:40,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Don't you ruin this for me!</i></font>

269
00:14:39,740 --> 00:14:40,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right.</font>

270
00:14:40,780 --> 00:14:43,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}I want to go have fun too!</i></font>

271
00:14:43,090 --> 00:14:45,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Get back here this instant!</i></font>

272
00:14:43,090 --> 00:14:45,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I ought to head back too.</font>

273
00:14:45,020 --> 00:14:45,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}That is all!</i></font>

274
00:14:45,540 --> 00:14:47,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}A-Apologies for that!</i></font>

275
00:14:47,280 --> 00:14:49,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The announcement booth was hijacked.</i></font>

276
00:14:51,230 --> 00:14:52,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why...?</font>

277
00:14:52,710 --> 00:14:55,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why the hell am I hiding?</font>

278
00:14:56,160 --> 00:14:58,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="20"><font face="Arial Black"><font color="#efff9f">MärChange</font></font></font></font>

279
00:14:57,250 --> 00:14:58,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry I'm late!</font>

280
00:14:58,660 --> 00:15:00,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're beyond late.</font>

281
00:15:00,170 --> 00:15:02,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}It's Alice! She's so cute!</font>

282
00:15:00,170 --> 00:15:01,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, sorry!</font>

283
00:15:01,870 --> 00:15:05,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was really bad because we didn't 
have enough people to cover the tables!</font>

284
00:15:05,280 --> 00:15:06,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miss, over here!</font>

285
00:15:06,840 --> 00:15:08,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Coming!</font>

286
00:15:10,630 --> 00:15:12,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sano? You changed?</font>

287
00:15:15,450 --> 00:15:16,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's up with him?</font>

288
00:15:18,310 --> 00:15:21,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Alice...</font>

289
00:15:22,380 --> 00:15:24,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for waiting!</font>

290
00:15:24,010 --> 00:15:25,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, is this girl here too?</font>

291
00:15:26,180 --> 00:15:29,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I bought it from that guy 
selling photos earlier.</font>

292
00:15:29,490 --> 00:15:32,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your class sure has a lot of hot girls.</font>

293
00:15:32,170 --> 00:15:33,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

294
00:15:33,180 --> 00:15:36,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm. She's okay, I guess.</font>

295
00:15:36,690 --> 00:15:38,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know that's Nanba-senpai, right?</font>

296
00:15:38,950 --> 00:15:40,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When he was a first-year.</font>

297
00:15:42,930 --> 00:15:44,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, lemme see that!</font>

298
00:15:44,710 --> 00:15:46,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me too, me too!</font>

299
00:15:48,010 --> 00:15:49,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The hell are you doin'?</font>

300
00:15:49,340 --> 00:15:50,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't get a look!</font>

301
00:15:52,760 --> 00:15:59,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wasn't expecting to run into this 
embarrassing relic while doing my rounds.</font>

302
00:16:00,420 --> 00:16:04,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Never thought my old library would 
see the light of day this quickly!</font>

303
00:16:06,180 --> 00:16:07,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That Nanba Minami...</font>

304
00:16:07,810 --> 00:16:09,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Always acting so high and mighty</font>

305
00:16:09,340 --> 00:16:11,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">just 'cause he's a little good-looking.</font>

306
00:16:11,420 --> 00:16:12,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He makes me sick.</font>

307
00:16:12,850 --> 00:16:16,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now he'll regret incurring my wrath!</font>

308
00:16:16,310 --> 00:16:18,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's the cause
 for celebration over here?</font>

309
00:16:20,820 --> 00:16:22,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nihonbashi...</font>

310
00:16:23,810 --> 00:16:26,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What? You got a problem?</font>

311
00:16:26,180 --> 00:16:29,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've got proper authorization!</font>

312
00:16:29,130 --> 00:16:31,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="14"><font color="#44443f"><b>This individual is authorized
 to vend independently.</b></font></font></font></font>

313
00:16:29,130 --> 00:16:31,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="18"><font color="#44443f"><b>Nihonbashi Wataru</b></font></font></font></font>

314
00:16:29,130 --> 00:16:31,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial Black"><font size="12"><font color="#44443f">Osaka High Festival Executive Committee</font></font></font></font>

315
00:16:31,760 --> 00:16:32,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah?</font>

316
00:16:33,390 --> 00:16:35,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ever hear of the right of publicity?</font>

317
00:16:38,550 --> 00:16:39,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know!</font>

318
00:16:40,610 --> 00:16:42,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why don't you enter 
the beauty pageant too?</font>

319
00:16:49,330 --> 00:16:52,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Just two hours remain in day two!</i></font>

320
00:16:52,530 --> 00:17:00,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="16"><font color="#8b7d91">Dorm 1\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hDorm 2\h\h\h\h\h\h\hDorm 3</font></font></font></font>

321
00:16:52,530 --> 00:16:53,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is our interim update.</i></font>

322
00:16:53,980 --> 00:16:55,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Dorm 1 has 104 points.</i></font>

323
00:16:55,950 --> 00:16:57,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Dorm 2 has 101 points.</i></font>

324
00:16:57,760 --> 00:16:59,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Dorm 3 has 110 points.</i></font>

325
00:16:59,650 --> 00:17:01,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Dorm 2 is dead last!</i></font>

326
00:17:03,810 --> 00:17:08,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess it makes sense that the artsy dorm
would dominate the second day.</font>

327
00:17:08,060 --> 00:17:11,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Apparently 3-B's haunted house
 is a huge hit.</font>

328
00:17:14,110 --> 00:17:16,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That tracks. Himejima, 
the Dorm 2 RA, is their class rep.</font>

329
00:17:16,820 --> 00:17:19,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Guess it's the real deal with make-up 
tech he learned in Hollywood</font>

330
00:17:19,800 --> 00:17:23,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and even projection mapping.</font>

331
00:17:23,780 --> 00:17:26,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn Masao...</font>

332
00:17:26,500 --> 00:17:29,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our mystery show isn't bad 
content-wise, but give me a break.</font>

333
00:17:30,780 --> 00:17:31,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Sano.</font>

334
00:17:33,570 --> 00:17:36,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Yang Guifei was really popular.</font>

335
00:17:36,930 --> 00:17:38,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're not doing it anymore?</font>

336
00:17:38,470 --> 00:17:39,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get lost.</font>

337
00:17:39,600 --> 00:17:42,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ooh, someone's in a mood.</font>

338
00:17:42,440 --> 00:17:47,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm busy. I've got no time for you.</font>

339
00:17:47,120 --> 00:17:49,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're not cute at all.</font>

340
00:17:49,660 --> 00:17:52,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just look at how Ashiya does it.</font>

341
00:17:53,540 --> 00:17:56,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Senpai, what are you doing?!</font>

342
00:17:56,090 --> 00:17:57,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How dare you, Nanba?!</font>

343
00:17:57,970 --> 00:17:59,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hands off!</font>

344
00:17:59,660 --> 00:18:01,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just playing.</font>

345
00:18:10,550 --> 00:18:11,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sano!</font>

346
00:18:12,040 --> 00:18:14,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll help you with the trash.</font>

347
00:18:14,700 --> 00:18:16,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Leave me the hell alone!</font>

348
00:18:16,400 --> 00:18:17,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's right over there.</font>

349
00:18:21,980 --> 00:18:25,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did I make him angry somehow?</font>

350
00:18:41,600 --> 00:18:45,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're saying you don't
understand how boys think?</font>

351
00:18:45,300 --> 00:18:49,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In fact, they're actually 
quite delicate beings.</font>

352
00:18:49,480 --> 00:18:54,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course there are things a tough
 girl like you wouldn't understand.</font>

353
00:18:54,320 --> 00:18:55,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that how it is?</font>

354
00:18:56,140 --> 00:18:58,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It is indeed.</font>

355
00:18:59,730 --> 00:19:02,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Speaking of, what happened with Minami?</font>

356
00:19:06,610 --> 00:19:08,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sounds like the kid's
 finally moving on, eh?</font>

357
00:19:10,440 --> 00:19:12,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He said that love matures,</font>

358
00:19:12,770 --> 00:19:15,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so he's got to grow up too.</font>

359
00:19:16,250 --> 00:19:19,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He also said I should
 tend my love with care.</font>

360
00:19:19,560 --> 00:19:21,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So that my feelings may bloom.</font>

361
00:19:22,340 --> 00:19:23,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a pompous little brat!</font>

362
00:19:25,900 --> 00:19:30,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, on that note, how are things 
going between you and Sano?</font>

363
00:19:32,490 --> 00:19:34,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you using protection like you should?</font>

364
00:19:36,530 --> 00:19:38,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not like that!</font>

365
00:19:38,140 --> 00:19:40,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sano doesn't even know I'm a woman!</font>

366
00:19:40,860 --> 00:19:43,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then what <i>is</i> it like?</font>

367
00:19:43,240 --> 00:19:44,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What do you mean?</font>

368
00:19:44,660 --> 00:19:46,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, he said I was...</font>

369
00:19:46,000 --> 00:19:48,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">a very important friend.</font>

370
00:19:48,750 --> 00:19:50,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which is...</font>

371
00:19:51,800 --> 00:19:53,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess that's fine for now.</font>

372
00:19:53,490 --> 00:19:56,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But there will come a time
 that's not enough.</font>

373
00:19:56,400 --> 00:19:57,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure.</font>

374
00:20:01,660 --> 00:20:03,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's such an idiot.</i></font>

375
00:20:04,980 --> 00:20:08,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's always been that way!</font>

376
00:20:08,790 --> 00:20:10,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the hell are you yelling for?</font>

377
00:20:14,690 --> 00:20:15,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sano...</font>

378
00:20:18,000 --> 00:20:20,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry for shouting at you earlier.</font>

379
00:20:20,870 --> 00:20:23,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was in a bad mood,
 and I took it out on you.</font>

380
00:20:26,970 --> 00:20:28,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's all. Nothing more.</font>

381
00:20:28,660 --> 00:20:29,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go.</font>

382
00:20:29,610 --> 00:20:32,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've still got to clean up 
and get ready for tomorrow.</font>

383
00:20:33,410 --> 00:20:34,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sano...</font>

384
00:20:36,390 --> 00:20:38,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hurry up if you don't want
 to get left behind.</font>

385
00:20:41,350 --> 00:20:42,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ashiya!</font>

386
00:20:45,050 --> 00:20:46,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you okay?</font>

387
00:20:46,050 --> 00:20:47,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you hurt?</font>

388
00:20:47,810 --> 00:20:48,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No...</font>

389
00:20:50,430 --> 00:20:51,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What happened?</font>

390
00:20:51,440 --> 00:20:52,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did a flowerpot fall?</font>

391
00:20:52,920 --> 00:20:54,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Holy crap, that was close!</font>

392
00:20:56,560 --> 00:20:58,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm scared to look up.</i></font>

393
00:20:58,790 --> 00:21:00,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What if there's someone there?</i></font>

394
00:21:04,740 --> 00:21:09,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Day two of our school festival 
has officially come to a close.</i></font>

395
00:21:11,600 --> 00:21:13,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm overthinking it.</font>

396
00:21:15,960 --> 00:21:19,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've checked Dorm 2 
two days in a row now!</font>

397
00:21:21,990 --> 00:21:23,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is your injury better?</font>

398
00:21:25,170 --> 00:21:27,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if getting hurt is part of the game,</font>

399
00:21:27,840 --> 00:21:30,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that guy belonged to our dorm.</font>

400
00:21:32,880 --> 00:21:34,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll call that round a draw.</font>

401
00:21:37,830 --> 00:21:39,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry about what happened.</font>

402
00:21:39,440 --> 00:21:42,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hear you'll be in the 
2,000-meter race tomorrow.</font>

403
00:21:42,000 --> 00:21:44,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll settle the score there for sure!</font>

404
00:21:45,630 --> 00:21:47,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We won't lose this time.</font>

405
00:21:48,500 --> 00:21:50,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still a big-mouthed brat, I see.</font>

406
00:21:50,970 --> 00:21:52,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go, Kitahanada!</font>

407
00:21:52,540 --> 00:21:53,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right!</font>

408
00:21:55,120 --> 00:21:57,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tennoji might actually be a decent guy.</font>

409
00:21:57,990 --> 00:22:00,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I heard a flowerpot fell.</font>

410
00:22:05,390 --> 00:22:06,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Better be careful.</font>

411
00:22:12,760 --> 00:22:14,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It couldn't be...</i></font>

412
00:23:45,370 --> 00:23:47,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sano, your Yang Guifei was so good!</font>

413
00:23:47,950 --> 00:23:50,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop it. I don't want any 
compliments for that.</font>

414
00:23:50,130 --> 00:23:52,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How should I put it?
The sensuality was off the charts!</font>

415
00:23:52,880 --> 00:23:54,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get those stars out of your eyes!</font>

416
00:23:54,360 --> 00:23:56,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I knew it. You have talent.</font>

417
00:23:56,210 --> 00:23:59,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What talent? And what do you mean,
 you knew it?!</font>

418
00:23:57,930 --> 00:23:59,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="20"><font face="Impact"><font color="#c7377d">Next Time</font></font></font></font>

419
00:23:57,930 --> 00:23:59,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Impact">{\an8}<font color="#c7377d">I Was the Same</font></font></font>

